Finally let us analyse the possibility of using the brane
potential energy of the scalar field  as the source of
acceleration now. We have seen that when matter is negligible on
the brane, one can build brane quintessence models. We now require
that this occurs only 
in the recent past. As can be expected, this leads to a fine-tuning
problem as 
 
